#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The tab bar, where you can switch through the open worksheets;"
msgid "The tab bar, where you can switch through the open worksheets."
msgstr "A barra de lapelas, na que se pode alternar entre as fichas abertas;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
