#, no-c-format
msgid "Completion"
msgstr "Completado"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled, &cantor; will show you possible completions for the "
"command you are currently typing when you press the Tab-key. If there is "
"only one choice remaining, it will insert the rest of the command for you."
msgstr ""
"Cando se activa isto, &cantor; mostra as posíbeis maneiras de completar a "
"orde que estás a escribir se premes a tecla TAB. Se só queda unha escolla, "
"insire automaticamente o resto da orde."

