#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Numbers"
msgstr "Números de liña"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether the different expressions should have a number "
"in front. This allows you to recall older results - in Maxima, for instance, "
"this is done with the <quote>%O1</quote> command."
msgstr ""
"Esta opción controla se as distintas expresións teñen un número diante. Isto "
"permite reutilizar resultados previos - no Maxima, por exemplo, isto faise "
"coa orde <quote>%01</quote>."

